	measure 'Infor Acquisition Rate (Sec Lots)' = ```
			
			var local =  if(SUM ( 'Securities Lots Fact'[Original Cost - Local] )=0,1,SUM ( 'Securities Lots Fact'[Original Cost - Local] ))
			return
			
			SWITCH(
			    TRUE(),
			    SELECTEDVALUE('Reporting Currency'[Rep in Currency])="SCD Base",SUM ( 'Securities Lots Fact'[Original Cost - Base] )/local,
			    SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "USD",SUMX ( 'Securities Lots Fact',RELATED('Fx Rate DQ'[USD BS Rate]) )/local,
			    SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "CAD",SUMX ( 'Securities Lots Fact',RELATED('Fx Rate DQ'[CAD BS Rate]) )/local,
			    SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) = "Company", SUMX ( 'Securities Lots Fact',RELATED('Fx Rate DQ'[FUNC BS Rate]) )/local,
			    SUMX ( 'Securities Lots Fact',RELATED('Fx Rate DQ'[HKD BS Rate]) )/local
			)
			
			```
		formatString: 0.000000
		lineageTag: d463c1dd-bc41-4090-929b-a21706c12b8b

