	measure 'Units (LH)' = ```
			
			VAR closePeriod =
			    MAX ( Period[Period] )
			VAR Dt =
			    CALCULATE (
			        SUM (
			            'Securities Lots Fact'[Nominal]
			        ),
			        ALL ( 'Period' ),
			        'Securities Lots Fact'[As Of Period] <= closePeriod
			    )
			RETURN
			    Dt
			
			```
		isHidden
		displayFolder: Lots Research Attributes
		lineageTag: f97657ea-a0c5-4e5a-9b2e-9e71eb721c23

